des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Light-Smart products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “Light-Smart” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “Light-Smart” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “Light-Smart” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bollard light.”
“Alexa, turn off the path light.”
“Alexa, set the smart light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the meteor light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the path light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set path light to green."
